{"word":"G4431 - πτῶσις - ptōsis - pto'-sis - Fall","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πτῶσις</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ptōsis"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pto'-sis"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Fall"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"விழுதல் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a falling, downfall"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From the alternate of <a href=\"#/G4098 - πίπτω - píptō - pip'-to/4098\">G4098</a>; a <i>crash</i>, that is, <i>downfall</i> (literally or figuratively): - fall."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1601 - ἐκπίπτω - ekpíptō - ek-pip'-to/1601\">G1601</a>, <a href=\"#/G2667 - καταπίπτω - katapíptō - kat-ap-ip'-to/2667\">G2667</a>, <a href=\"#/G3895 - παραπίπτω - parapíptō - par-ap-ip'-to/3895\">G3895</a>, <a href=\"#/G3900 - παράπτωμα - paráptōma - par-ap'-to-mah/3900\">G3900</a>, <a href=\"#/G4045 - περιπίπτω - peripíptō - per-ee-pip'-to/4045\">G4045</a>, <a href=\"#/G4098 - πίπτω - píptō - pip'-to/4098\">G4098</a>, <a href=\"#/G4430 - πτῶμα - ptōma - pto'-mah/4430\">G4430</a>, <a href=\"#/G4431 - πτῶσις - ptōsis - pto'-sis/4431\">G4431</a>, <a href=\"#/G4432 - πτωχεία - ptōcheía - pto-khi'-ah/4432\">G4432</a>, <a href=\"#/G4433 - πτωχεύω - ptōcheúō - pto-khyoo'-o/4433\">G4433</a>, <a href=\"#/G4434 - πτωχός - ptōchós - pto-khos'/4434\">G4434</a>"}]}